title: Bus Simulator 2013 v2.0
description:
Bus Simulator 2013 offers you a wonderful game experience! The Game provides a lot of new buses and missions!

GAME FEATURES:

- 33 Different Buses
- 2 Huge Cities
- 20 Missions / Level
- Different Graphic settings
- Steering option with 3 different Steering
- NO In-App Purchase / Everything is free and included in this game
